## Training Tips for MD Trajectory Data

- **Data augmentation** helps because MD renders can have varied lighting/orientations
- **Small batch sizes** (8–16) work well if GPU memory is limited
- **Transfer learning** from COCO weights converges faster than training from scratch
- **Early stopping** (patience=20) prevents wasted compute after the optimal epoch

